## Funding Pools

A collective can open a **funding pool**: an arrangement through which members fund shared [AI agents](/help/agents) together, governed by one baseline rule — pool money is only ever spent on activity every pool member can see. Enrollment is a separate, explicit step from membership, each call bills one enrolled member's prepaid balance within consented ceilings, and the pool itself never holds funds. See [Funding Pools](/help/funding-pools) for the full picture: the visibility rule, enrollment and withdrawal, draw mechanics, and admin controls.

